The current items displayed appear to be mostly clothing items like tank tops, bodysuits, and swimwear, which could be considered sports/athletic wear. All the prices I see are well under $100 (ranging from $0.01 to $1.08 on this first page).

I notice in the price filter section on the left side, there's an option for '$0.00 - $999.99' which has 874 items. This is too broad for my specific requirement of 'under $100'.
